BB%B3-09/poem-wN45DJ0ZB5nlxoJKmQBbvA">Thập bất hài kỳ 09 - 十不諧其九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-Minh-%C3%A2u/poem-WlcrTsqqVcOiF32NrBuFLA">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - Minh âu - 水調歌頭－盟鷗</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-Kh%E1%BA%A5u/V%C3%A3n-Ho%C3%A0-Th%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-et9KlKexXTNBy4XwOT7YcA">Vãn Hoà Thân kỳ 1 - 挽和珅其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-Kh%E1%BA%A5u/author-svMQDOV_e4vEtYCGO8gq1g">Đậu Khấu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-04/poem-82wx8VAIFRM62TxBEXxf4Q">Xuân nhật tuyệt cú thập thủ kỳ 04 - 春日絕句十首其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
